<div class="modal w500" id="js-image-select-panel" style="z-index:9999">
    <div class="modal-header">
        <button type="button" class="close">&times;</button>
        <h4>图片管理</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-body img-list-middle">
        <div class="row-fluid bottom-line">
            <div class="span9">图片格式仅支持jpg,jpeg,png,gif格式,大小不超过1M,或者您也可以从您的图片库中选择图片,选中后点击【确定】。</div>
            <div class="span3">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="image-upload-btn">上传图片</button>
                <input id="image-upload" style="display: none" type="file" name="file">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span9">
                <select>
                    <option>所有图片</option>
                    <option>宝贝图片</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="span3">
                <a href="javascript:void(0)"> 图片空间管理</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="image-list">
            <div class="row-fluid">
                {{#each data.data}}
                <div class="span2">
                    <img src="{{url}}">
                </div>
                {{#mod @index 6}}
                </div>
                <div class="row-fluid ">
                {{/mod}}
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="modal-footer">
        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span8">
                <div id="image-pagination" class="jq-pagination" data-total={{data.total}}></div>
            </div>
            <div class="span2">
                <button class="btn cancel">取消</button>
            </div>
            <div class="span2">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" id="js-image-choose-ok">确定</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
